{"tid":1862134,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"傳金像獎取消　田啟文：繼續舉行但規模縮細","createTime":"2020-02-04T12:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T02:11:59.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee5c7e48950f44de6c03ece1d603ce9e12ab628","tid":1862134,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T12:58:01.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情肆虐，不少大型活動都被迫要取消，早前有傳原定4月19日舉行的香港電影金像獎亦將取消。據本地媒體報道，金像獎董事局董事田啟文澄清，金像獎會繼續舉行，但規模會縮細，亦會取消行紅地毯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n田啟文透露，為了減少人流聚集，將減少邀請頒獎嘉賓和得獎人以外的嘉賓，地點亦由尖沙咀文化中心，改為場地較細的九龍灣國際展貿中心。<br />\n<br />\n至於原定2月12日公布各大獎項的提名名單的記者會，亦將改以網上公布。"},{"pid":"9795a7cbb77ae02d9efc80de60b29d0903af2558","tid":1862134,"uid":132587,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:43:08.000Z","msg":"仲敢搞肯撚定攬炒<br />\n成班唔戴口罩 你知香港幾多藝人幾奶共成日番大陸"},{"pid":"db80613398f21a7c54b01bfc7168c6f45f84e01e","tid":1862134,"uid":174283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:30:46.000Z","msg":"佢做錯嘢咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c589d5d58df3e73dbc70414eddc93428731efe0f","tid":1862134,"uid":35221,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:39:10.000Z","msg":"有個留言好笑：不如喺酒樓搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b081e19681784153a5a07b995712b20e30f0cd5d","tid":1862134,"uid":313584,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c589d5d58df3e73dbc70414eddc93428731efe0f","tid":1862134,"uid":35221,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:39:10.000Z","msg":"有個留言好笑：不如喺酒樓搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:45:43.000Z","msg":"生財龍蝦宴<br />\n金像乳豬賀影帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c3f6bd513ca57187b596eb1d664c5919c1696a","tid":1862134,"uid":143582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c589d5